{"tid":1708222,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶］藍屍傷左咁多手足政府都無割蓆，今日火燒藍屍你地就想割？","createTime":"2019-11-11T13:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:09:41.000Z","uid":262035,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0ab6751e228608d46621ffa074879f3d4da9b242","tid":1708222,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:45:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家係咪唔記得咗有幾多手足比藍屍斬啦？<br />\n政府又出嚟譴責過幾多次呀？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">係無呀屌你老母！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>7.21</strong></span> 近百個元朗鄉黑以藤條及木棍，無差別攻擊元朗西鐵站既乘客，<span style=\"color: red;\">最少45人受傷，部份人傷勢嚴重</span>。最終只拘捕34個鄉黑，當中只有6人被控暴動罪。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>8.5</strong></span> 40個福建幫於荃灣襲擊示威者，有<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者被斬斷手筋腳筋至見骨，左腳肌肉幾乎全被斬斷，將永久失去知覺，未肯定活動能力能否復原</span>。施襲者未被拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">8.20</span></strong> 藍屍於將軍澳連儂隧道，<span style=\"color: red;\">持刀襲擊3名男女，其中2人情況嚴重</span>。施襲者被控3項傷人罪。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10.6</span></strong> 藍屍的士司機被困於九龍遊行的人潮中時，突然加速撞向路邊示威者，<span style=\"color: red;\">2名女子被撞傷，其中一人雙腳骨折，情況嚴重</span>。涉事司機未被拘捕，更獲贈52萬捐款。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">10.19</span></strong> 持雙程證刀手於大埔連儂牆斬傷一名正派發文宣既19歲學生，<span style=\"color: red;\">學生後腦及腹部受傷，腸臟露出</span>。刀手自首後因傷人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>11.3</strong></span> 藍屍刀手係太古城咬甩趙家賢既耳廓，並斬傷多人，<span style=\"color: red;\">至少6人受傷，其中一名男子身中9刀，導致氣胸及腸臟受損，情況一度危殆</span>。刀手最終被控傷人罪。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">仲有更多藍屍傷人事件未能盡錄</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應承我都唔割手足蓆呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"7a4d234da020c30ab816b21cf49bc1a9a3bf1042","tid":1708222,"uid":311796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"冇人想割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5ec8830cdf6765e4c6faf96a178ae6c186d7fc","tid":1708222,"uid":198392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:49:42.000Z","msg":"幼稚園都要番全日放5點？痴撚線藍絲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1707636/page/1?post=1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1707636/page/1?post=1</a>"},{"pid":"cf9decc42ec175b1189f694c2792137701146000","tid":1708222,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:50:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763c1ce751dd9d32abe2dce2936a9468da9300dc","tid":1708222,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7a4d234da020c30ab816b21cf49bc1a9a3bf1042","tid":1708222,"uid":311796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:46:28.000Z","msg":"冇人想割<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"想勾起返大家啲記憶<br />\n記返藍屍傷左幾多手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好成日在意畫面好唔好睇或者政府講乜啦！"},{"pid":"09f65ec61d0c0e4ae7987455dc682c4be31681d2","tid":1708222,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:57:08.000Z","msg":"原來有異議都叫割蓆<br />\n仲拎自己同班低等藍屍比"},{"pid":"a2825a1762f3cd58260cc32184dcefca2ddd8c36","tid":1708222,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T13:57:43.000Z","msg":"藍屍表示: 睇唔到"},{"pid":"9cc2c0ee527927032067843a8a725021e33f6e4c","tid":1708222,"uid":94978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee24fd449ba7e8e06fafd83bf5e24570c0dc1c72","tid":1708222,"uid":335936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:03:18.000Z","msg":"無割！"},{"pid":"bbae208201da0f9a7fd2c7adac76ec913cb19d14","tid":1708222,"uid":314132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPhksRj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPhksRj.jpg&h=92e04e51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9e8fefb341c855a592ab6a5e0528a3bc638a24b","tid":1708222,"uid":222305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"特技人出黎曬太陽<br />\n曬黑左小小之嗎<br />\n可能重有人工收呀！<br />\n燒乜鳩？割乜鳩？<br />\n其他野我乜都唔知道！我見唔到！"},{"pid":"387f7d471ce5b739e7c4eec3b517dbbbb22356e4","tid":1708222,"uid":267753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T14:09:41.000Z","msg":"割條毛"}]}